This widget are packaged to support several widget systems.

First of all; the player is mainly intended to follow the W3C Widget specification.
Sadly not all follow this specification. Shame on them!! This file is intended to keep track of what file
belong to each packaging system.

Common player files and directories:
- css
- fonts
- gfx
- script
- index.html
- README


Files belonging to the W3C Widget specification - http://www.w3.org/TR/widgets/:
- config.xml


Files belonging to the Apple Desktop Widget specification - http://developer.apple.com/macosx/dashboard.html:
- Default.png
- Icon.png
- Info.plist